                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white/15 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-white/20"><svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-sky-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m21 7.5-9-5.25L3 7.5m18 0-9 5.25m9-5.25v9l-9 5.25M3 7.5l9 5.25M3 7.5v9l9 5.25m0-9v9"/></svg>Matrix Generator (envs &times; services)</span>
                    <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white/15 backdrop-blur px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg border border-white/20"><svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5 text-emerald-200" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.023 9.348h4.992v-.001M2.985 19.644v-4.992m0 0h4.992m-4.993 0 3.181 3.183a8.25 8.25 0 0 0 13.803-3.7M4.031 9.865a8.25 8.25 0 0 1 13.803-3.7l3.181 3.182"/></svg>Auto-sync + Self-heal</span>
